name: MyBirthday
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my birthday
des:
Welcome to My Birthday skill

-This skill asks the user to add their birthday, and after adding the user's birthday it keeps track of the birthday and tells how many days left for the birthday.
-You have to give month, day, and year so that Alexa can precisely tell you the remaining time for your birthday and how old you will be.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
